### 2. Reduced-Form VAR(1)

Estimated on 1985M2–2019M12 (418 observations). Ordering: EPU, PAYEMS growth, INDPRO growth, PCEPI growth.

#### 2d. Estimated equations

```
epu_t      = 46.067 + 0.641·epu_{t-1} − 19.313·payems_g_{t-1} − 3.540·indpro_g_{t-1} − 13.225·pcepi_g_{t-1} + u_epu,t

payems_g_t = 0.058 − 0.000278·epu_{t-1} + 0.679·payems_g_{t-1} + 0.017·indpro_g_{t-1} + 0.033·pcepi_g_{t-1} + u_payems,t

indpro_g_t = 0.111 − 0.001·epu_{t-1} + 0.925·payems_g_{t-1} + 0.073·indpro_g_{t-1} + 0.458·pcepi_g_{t-1} + u_indpro,t

