![Unconditional INDPRO](output/unco_indpro.png)

**Figure note (Figure 4):** Unconditional forecast for month-on-month industrial production growth (INDPRO). Same specification as Figure 3.

Both series show growth increasing over the forecast horizon, consistent with the VAR's mean-reversion dynamics.

